Example Claim SubType Codes

This value set includes sample Claim SubType codes which are used to distinguish the claim types for example within type institutional there may be subtypes for emergency services, bedstay and transportation.

Copyright Statement: This is an example set.

This value set includes codes from the following code systems:

  • Include all codes defined in http://hl7.org/fhir/ex-claimsubtype
